      <section id="section_knn_3kg_rzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Purpose</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To define a work instruction for the installation and setup of a proximity sensor
            (OIS-03261). The sensor must be properly aligned on the feeder mechanism so that the
            system can accurately detect the relationship between the shear cut and the rotation of
            the Servo Gob Distributor.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="section_kzs_3kg_rzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Application</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">This work instruction applies to Space manufacturing facilities, and is required on all
            Servo Gob Distributor installations with mechanical feeder mechanisms.</p>
      </section>
